== Language (compiler and runtime)
- <If ...> ... <Else> ...
  <*AAAA, !*BBBB> == <If *AAAA, !*BBBB>
  <Else ...> is like <ElseIf ...>
- ImportData, ImportDataPush stdlib
- Support "{File}"
- Support TAP SubTests
- Foo = ... assignment for TestML vars can
  - Only support TestML approved vars
  - Type check them

== Compiler
- Fix Pegex bugs
- Support `_` in var names and bridge method names
  - Or make _ throw appropriate compile error
- Support source mapping
  - Use in labels
- Support === with no (empty) label
- %ImportData compiler feature
- %Import  (...compiler fix...)
  - With or without .tml suffix
  - Multinode name should be 'foo/bar'
    - Look under $TESTML_PATH and then $TESTML_DIR
- Fix foo.bar:baz precedence bug
  - *foo.bar.Catch:msg
- Honor and enforce %TestML statement
- Nested functions
  - Make work with subtests

